Exxaro ‘Looking at All Options’ After Noble Territory Offer

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-06-09T08:44:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/exxaro-looking-at-all-options-after-noble-territory-offer-1-.html
Exxaro Resources Ltd. (EXX)  is “looking at
all options” after Noble Group Ltd. outbid the South African
company on a deal to buy  Territory Resources Ltd. (TTY) , Exxaro
spokesman Hilton Atkinson said.  Exxaro, in a statement today, urged Territory shareholders
not to take any action until it reviews its position. Exxaro
said the Noble bid will remain open until July 21.  Territory shares rose 11 percent to 52 cents at the 4:10
p.m. close of trading on the Australian Stock Exchange  To contact the reporter on this story:
Carli Lourens in Johannesburg at 
